data.description:
Welcome to your new home sweet home! This delightful bi-level residence offers comfort, convenience, and a warm ambiance that you'll adore.
Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this charming bi-level home is the perfect place to create lasting memories. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, it offers a comfortable and inviting living space for your family.
Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the warm and welcoming atmosphere. The main level features a spacious living and dining area, perfect for gatherings and entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze.
Downstairs, the lower-level family room provides a cozy retreat for movie nights or relaxation. With a convenient half bath on this level, you'll appreciate the added convenience.
The three bedrooms on the upper level are generously sized, offering comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation. The full bathroom is conveniently located nearby.
Outside, the attached garage provides extra storage space. The backyard has plenty of room to play, garden, or host barbecues with family and friends.
Located in the heart of Surfside Eastlake, you'll enjoy easy access to local schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful bi-level house your forever home!
Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and charm of this Eastlake gem for yourself. Your new beginning awaits!
